---
// Hero Section - Full Width con Parallax y slider de imágenes
---

<section id="home" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
  <div class="relative w-full h-screen md:h-[70vh] overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Slider con Parallax -->
    <div class="hero-background absolute inset-0 w-full h-full">
      <div class="slider-container relative w-full h-full">
        <img
          src="/nails/store-colors-manicure.webp"
          alt="Tienda Paula Nails 1"
          class="slider-image absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center transition-opacity duration-1000"
          fetchpriority="high"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
        <img
          src="/nails/store-hair.webp"
          alt="Tienda Paula Nails 2"
          class="slider-image absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center transition-opacity duration-1000 opacity-0"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
        <img
          src="/nails/store-colors-manicure.webp"
          alt="Tienda Paula Nails 3"
          class="slider-image absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center transition-opacity duration-1000 opacity-0"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
        <img
          src="/nails/store-manicure.webp"
          alt="Tienda Paula Nails 4"
          class="slider-image absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center transition-opacity duration-1000 opacity-0"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
      <!-- Overlay oscuro para mejor contraste -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: var(--overlay-dark);">
      </div>

      <!-- Gradiente difuminado inferior para integración suave -->
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-12 md:h-16 pointer-events-none"
        style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 0%, rgba(236, 212, 226, 0.1) 60%, var(--background) 100%);"
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contenido del Hero centrado -->
    <div
      class="hero-content relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center h-screen md:h-[70vh] px-4"
    >
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Logo Principal -->
        <h1
          class="text-white text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-medium text-pretty leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-6"
        >
          Paula <br />
          <span class="font-edwardian">Nails</span>
        </h1>

        <!-- Texto rotativo shiny -->
        <h2
          class="text-white text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8"
        >
          <span class="shiny-sec rotating-text font-semibold"></span>
        </h2>

        <!-- Descripción -->
        <p
          class="text-white text-base md:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed"
        >
          Centro de estética y belleza en Alcalá de Henares especializado en
          manicura, pedicura y diseño de uñas. Tratamientos profesionales con
          los mejores productos del mercado.
        </p>

        <!-- Social Icons & CTA Button -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center"
        >
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="https://www.instagram.com/paulanails.es?igsh=MWIxZjNyOXdzbHp1Nw=="
              aria-label="Instagram"
              style="color: var(--icon-color); border-color: var(--border-light); background-color: var(--pink-light);"
              class="hover:text-white transition duration-300 ease-in-out border border-1 p-2 md:p-3 rounded-xl"
